title: gen 8 pokemon are real & here
body:
those starters look ADORABLE. Like, this is a generation where I’d legit have difficulty choosing.

now i’m holding out hope that we get the tradition of a new eevee evolution.
dragon, flying, poison, bug, ghost, steel, ground, fighting, rock, any of them would be cool.

summary: The new starters are cute af but can we talk about the new region??? Like damn it’s so gorgeous it’s my exact favorite aesthetic...
body:
The new starters are cute af but can we talk about the new region??? Like damn it’s so gorgeous it’s my exact favorite aesthetic aka the idyllic England countryside, featuring both quaint ivy-covered cottages and industrial cities with cogs and large clock towers

I’m in LOVE I am going to spend precisely 90% of my time playing this game just looking at the scenery
